snippet.title: Tinertia Slums Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Hardcore platforming: No Jump Button! Geared for the new generation of streamers with easy to pick-up but tough to master mechanics, Tinertia challenges players to master the powerful rocket launcher to control the momentum, rhythm, speed, and rocket-jump Weldon over deadly obstacles, outrun robo-bosses, and ultimately escape off the planet.

http://www.tinertia.com/
